{
  "name": "phi-psd-brochure-and-kastner-engagements-1969-1972-b8d001",
  "title": "PHI Computer Services Professional Services Division: Brochure with Kastner Profile, Memoir of Junior Programmer Era, and PHI Engagements (1969-1972)",
  "description": "Combines a primary-source PHI Update brochure (~1971-1972) describing PHI's Professional Services Division (PSD) \u2014 including Kastner's profile as a Systems Analyst in the Financial Systems Group \u2014 with Kastner's personal memoir of his March 1969 entry into PHI as a junior programmer at $7,200/year, the 1960s-era apprenticeship learning model, and his work on Marine Midland bond-portfolio Y2K-precursor changes, the First Chicago correspondent-bank DDA system, the Cumberland Farms gas-station accounting system, and the optimization of PHI's internal accounting system.",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "created": "2026-04-25",
